        <div class="text-color-text-low-emphasis text-md [&amp;&gt;*]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;*]:text-md [&amp;&gt;*]:text-color-text-low-emphasis">
          
          
    <div class="show-more-less-text">
      <p class="show-more-less-text__text--less">
        Built and deployed a production-style solar energy forecasting platform that predicts next 48 hour solar energy generation (kWh) using machine learning and real-time weather inputs.<br>• Engineered feature pipeline using research-grade solar and climate datasets<br>• Designed day-grouped temporal validation strategy to prevent data leakage<br>• Compared Linear Regression, Ridge Regression, and LightGBM models<br>• Applied hyperparameter tuning and evaluated performance using MAE, RMSE, and…
            

    
    

    <button class="show-more-less-text__button show-more-less-button
        show-more-less-text__button--more" data-tracking-control-name="public_profile_project-description_show-more-text-btn" aria-label="Show more details for Solar Drishti — End-to-End Solar Energy Forecasting System" aria-expanded="false">
        Show more

          <icon class="show-more-less-text__button-icon show-more-less-button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static.licdn.com/aero-v1/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo"></icon>
    </button>
  
      </p>

        <p class="show-more-less-text__text--more" tabindex="-1">
          Built and deployed a production-style solar energy forecasting platform that predicts next 48 hour solar energy generation (kWh) using machine learning and real-time weather inputs.<br>• Engineered feature pipeline using research-grade solar and climate datasets<br>• Designed day-grouped temporal validation strategy to prevent data leakage<br>• Compared Linear Regression, Ridge Regression, and LightGBM models<br>• Applied hyperparameter tuning and evaluated performance using MAE, RMSE, and R²<br>• Normalized target variable (capacity-adjusted energy) to improve generalization<br>• Integrated serialized LightGBM model into Django backend for real-time inference<br>• Designed scalable architecture separating data preparation, training, and runtime layers<br>• Deployed live application on Render with PostgreSQL integration<br>Developed collaboratively with team members who led frontend development, Django backend implementation, and deployment configuration.<br>Tech Stack: Python, Scikit-learn, LightGBM, Django, PostgreSQL, Pandas
            

    
    

    <button class="show-more-less-text__button show-more-less-button
