          Solar PV &amp; Weather Data Engineering Pipeline
      
        </h3>

            <h4 class="text-color-text text-md [&amp;&gt;*]:mb-0 not-first-middot leading-[1.75]">
                
        
                  
    
    
    
    
    
    

      <span class="date-range text-color-text-secondary font-sans text-md leading-open font-regular">
