        <div class="text-color-text-low-emphasis text-md [&amp;&gt;*]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;*]:text-md [&amp;&gt;*]:text-color-text-low-emphasis">
          
          
    <div class="show-more-less-text">
      <p class="show-more-less-text__text--less">
        Designed and implemented a complete data pipeline to construct an hourly solar PV production dataset enriched with historical weather features for machine learning applications.<br>The pipeline processes large-scale NREL synthetic distributed PV (DPV) datasets, selectively extracting relevant files, parsing system metadata (latitude, longitude, capacity) embedded in filenames, and transforming 5-minute power output data into an hourly resolution.<br>Due to the absence of a unified dataset…
            

    
    

    <button class="show-more-less-text__button show-more-less-button
        show-more-less-text__button--more" data-tracking-control-name="public_profile_project-description_show-more-text-btn" aria-label="Show more details for Solar PV &amp;amp; Weather Data Engineering Pipeline" aria-expanded="false">
        Show more

          <icon class="show-more-less-text__button-icon show-more-less-button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static.licdn.com/aero-v1/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo"></icon>
    </button>
  
      </p>

        <p class="show-more-less-text__text--more" tabindex="-1">
          Designed and implemented a complete data pipeline to construct an hourly solar PV production dataset enriched with historical weather features for machine learning applications.<br>The pipeline processes large-scale NREL synthetic distributed PV (DPV) datasets, selectively extracting relevant files, parsing system metadata (latitude, longitude, capacity) embedded in filenames, and transforming 5-minute power output data into an hourly resolution.<br>Due to the absence of a unified dataset containing PV system size, production output, and weather data, historical NCDB hourly weather data (GHI, DNI, DHI, air temperature, wind speed, solar zenith angle) was programmatically fetched, spatially aligned using grid-based aggregation, and merged with PV generation data.<br>The repository emphasizes clean data engineering practices, including environment-variable based configuration, structured scripts, licensing compliance, and exclusion of raw data from version control.<br>This dataset serves as the foundational data layer for the Solar Drishti project.
            

    
    

    <button class="show-more-less-text__button show-more-less-button
