        Built a Java-based console matchmaking system as a team project, focusing on backend logic, secure user onboarding, and database-driven workflows.<br>The system supports account creation with 20+ validated attributes, including optional profile fields, OTP-based email verification, and session-based login handling. Each user attribute is validated individually to ensure data integrity and consistency.<br>Implemented profile editing, preference-based match discovery (age range, city, combined…
            

    
    

    <button class="show-more-less-text__button show-more-less-button
        show-more-less-text__button--more" data-tracking-control-name="public_profile_project-description_show-more-text-btn" aria-label="Show more details for MatchMate – Java-Based Matchmaking System" aria-expanded="false">
